<image id="img_id3158407" src="sw/imglst/sc20238.png" width="5.64mm" height="5.64mm"><alt id="alt_id3158407" xml-lang="en-US">Icon</alt>
	</image></paragraph>
</tablecell>
<tablecell colspan="" rowspan="">
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3156422" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="14">If you drag objects out of the <link href="text/shared/guide/navigator.xhp" name="Navigator"><emph>Navigator</emph></link>, you can specify in the submenu of the Navigator's <emph>Drag Mode</emph> icon whether to copy the object, insert it as a link or insert it as a hyperlink.</paragraph>
</tablecell>
</tablerow>
</table>

<paragraph role="tip" id="par_id3153144" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">You can cancel a drag-and-drop operation in $[officename] at any time by pressing the Esc key before releasing the mouse button.</paragraph>
